{"tid":1616039,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[殘體字文化Alert]  蒙面 定 幪面","createTime":"2019-10-03T09:25:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T06:34:00.000Z","uid":187489,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"11ac6812382a34aa8625b9aeb80c510f926b61d5","tid":1616039,"uid":187489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T09:25:16.000Z","msg":"屌你老母mon po狗<br />\n你老婆俾狗屌緊呀 打電話check下啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2360000/2364269/e2a2f50f-01df-4f3b-b9ba-bc243c611829_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2360000%2F2364269%2Fe2a2f50f-01df-4f3b-b9ba-bc243c611829_1024.jpg&h=01c73f1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">由幾時開始 全港media都用<br />\n「蒙面」取代「幪面」<br />\n<br />\n蒙面可能唔係殘體，但一定唔係香港用開嘅字</span></span><br />\n<br />\n仲記得幾年前鄰國套蒙面歌王，覺得個名好唔順眼，到左呢幾個月俾media搞到睇慣左，<br />\n<br />\n就好似好多人真係唔小心順口將鐳射筆講左做鐳射槍一樣<br />\n<br />\n有錯請指正<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">拒絕被洗腦呀大家！！！！</span><br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非：</span><br />\n喺街見到人借locker要帶<span style=\"color: pink;\">鎖</span><br />\n有人口渴要帶<span style=\"color: pink;\">罐裝飲品</span><br />\n病左最起碼要<span style=\"color: pink;\">戴口罩</span><br />\n喺示威地區附近行街要<span style=\"color: pink;\">戴豬嘴</span><br />\n樣衰要<span style=\"color: pink;\">遮樣/遮耳</span><br />\n顯瘦要<span style=\"color: red;\">全黑</span><br />\n潮人着衫要fast fashion：<span style=\"color: pink;\">越平越好</span>，有螢光粉都<span style=\"color: pink;\">可以即棄</span>，Apple Watch 買平錶帶，換過條都唔肉赤<br />\n想靚靚就要着純色<span style=\"color: pink;\">冇brand、冇logo、唔好戴accessories</span><br />\n秋風起，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">着風褸笠住個頭防色防粉防水防露髮型耳仔</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"217d9e8b8a28660f270a323eb